-- Shanghai Stock Exchange Is `Actively Promoting' ETF Listings, Zhang Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-26T09:33:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-26/shanghai-stock-exchange-is-actively-promoting-etf-listings-zhang-says.html

          
          
             The Shanghai Stock Exchange is
“actively” promoting listings of exchange-traded funds and
studying allowing foreign companies to issue yuan-denominated
bonds, Zhang Yujun, president of the bourse, said at a forum in
Shanghai.  
